g" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Aaj8DhB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iznbFAq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0er5kUO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hZG2YJA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UzKe4zg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>“We’d do anything to protect our kids” “okay pick policies that might raise your taxes” “NEVER” it’s really starting to get old and I’m so tired and literally nothing changes. I’m scared for my kid, and none of this is helping that. 

The most frustrating part: husband is pro gun. When I asked him if he still was he basically said he’s scared to give them up because republicans/cops could still come for us and in situations like Ukraine they couldn’t distribute guns fast enough. Imagine being so scared in your own country that you won’t even consider giving up weapons to stop children being hunted for sport. 

Idk. I just feel like I’m sitting here screaming and no one cares. This is like the fifth gigantic traumatizing event I’ve suffered through because Texas and/or the US sucks (I grew up going to Uvalde all the time so this hits really hard, and also worked in disaster relief, huge yikes) and I am sick of being called selfish by my family when I talk about moving to a country where CHILDREN DONT DIE.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PxmuLXu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kirbyvictorious]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Heartbroken</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eFTd3Oo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dxsD3K6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>this one's a blast from the past https://loadingartist.com/comic/heartbroken</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eFTd3Oo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[loadingartist]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>All dogs are good</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7KGQ5G7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ceuza7g.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7KGQ5G7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dogspost]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Some love it, some hate it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/opdxV7F</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s0V4T9D.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#dog #cute #cute_animal #funny_animal #mildly_interesting #aww #wholesome #adorable #lol</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/opdxV7F</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[charizardkitty]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Didn’t know I liked this song until now</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1aJRhDk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gHZB7ZW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span><